We will install 1 emergency water safety switch and new digital thermostat.

This option includes the replacement of breaker or fuses per manufacture specs.

response.description: This service includes the professional installation of a 200-foot Govee Pro RGBIC smart lighting system, mounted using custom SnapTrack aluminum channels for a clean, permanent appearance. Designed for year-round use, this lighting solution is ideal for holiday displays, architectural accents, or everyday exterior illumination.  Scope of Work:  200 Feet of Govee Pro Smart LED Lighting Lighting is installed along eaves, fascia, or rooflines based on the homeâ€™s layout and customer preference. Each section is measured, cut, and secured for a seamless and long-lasting result.  Custom SnapTrack Aluminum Mounting Channels Tracks are precision-cut and securely fastened to the home exterior. Color-matched where applicable, they provide a professional finish while concealing and protecting all wiring.  Concealed Wiring and Cable Management All wiring is routed within the aluminum track system or through soffits to keep the installation visually clean and protected from environmental exposure.  Weatherproof Junction Box Installation A junction box is installed near the roof edge or in the soffit to house the Govee controller and electrical connections. The box is fully sealed for weather resistance and long-term reliability.  New GFCI Outdoor Outlet with Weatherproof Cover Includes the installation of a new GFCI-protected outlet. Power is run from the nearest code-compliant source, and the outlet is equipped with a weatherproof bubble cover to ensure safety and code compliance.  Controller and Smart App Integration The Govee controller is mounted inside the junction box or another discrete location. response.description:
This service includes the professional installation of a Govee 4-pack smart up-lighting system designed to illuminate columns, palm trees, or landscape features.
    Our installation focuses on clean placement, concealed wiring, and a durable, weather-resistant setup that enhances curb appeal day or night.

    Included in This Service:

    • Placement & Mounting of Govee Up Lights
      Lights installed at optimal angles for balanced, even illumination on columns, trunks, or foliage.

    • Concealed Wiring & Cable Management
      All wiring neatly routed along landscape edges, behind structures, or lightly trenched where needed to remain hidden and protected.

This service includes the professional installation of a 200-foot Govee Pro smart lighting system with custom SnapTrack aluminum channels for a sleek, permanent appearance. Designed for all-season use, this lighting system is ideal for accent lighting, holiday displays, or everyday architectural illumination.
Our installation ensures a fully integrated, weatherproof, and secure system from start to finish, using top-tier materials and methods to protect all components from the elements.
  • 200 Feet of Govee Pro Smart LED Lighting
    Installed along eaves, roof lines, or fascia as specified.


  • Custom SnapTrack Aluminum Mounting Channels
    Precision-cut, color-matched (where applicable), and securely fastened to the home exterior. Channels hide and protect all wiring, offering a clean, professional finish.


  • Concealed Wiring & Cable Management
    All lighting cables are routed inside tracks and/or through soffits to remain hidden and protected.


  • Weatherproof Junction Box Installation
    Mounted either within the soffit or just outside at the roof edge. Houses all automation control systems and connection points for reliable, low-profile access.


  • New GFCI Outlet Installation (With Weatherproof Cover)
    A dedicated outdoor-rated outlet is run from the nearest power source to the junction box, complete with a weatherproof bubble cover and GFCI protection to meet code compliance and ensure safety.


  • Controller & Smart App Integration
    Govee controller housed inside the junction box or discrete location. Basic setup and pairing with the customer’s mobile device is included, ensuring easy use and automation of lighting.
